resources.string: Ho Chi Minh city National University

The Ho Chi Minh Communist Youth Union and the Vietnamese Student Association have long been names familiar to all young people and students in the country. Since its inception to date, Organization of the Union - Association has always affirmed its position, is the representative of young and influential people affects many domestic and international organizations. In particular, in the current integration period, As English becomes the popular language in many countries around the world, then it became necessary to unify common terms in English to be possible exchange information with international friends about the Union - Association work. From that reality, Youth Union - Student Association of University of Economics - Construction Law building the Dictionary of the Union - Association. Through this dictionary we hope that this will be Effective tools to help you Union, Students in particular School and Union, Student City members in general can apply to the work of Union - Association and in life.
